Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of relaying techniques in ARQ mechanisms and focuses on the link quality control mechanism for selective and opportunistic AF relaying in cooperative ARQs. This topic falls under the intersection of several computer science sub-disciplines, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and multimedia (cs.MM).
